OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1777367169
OL,3,CHow a 97g 'super shoe' helped make
OL,4,Cmarathon history in London
OL,6,FKenya's Sabastian Sawe made history at
OL,7,Fthe London Marathon on Sunday by
OL,8,Fbecoming the first athlete to run a
OL,9,Fcompetitive marathon in under two
OL,10,Fhours.
OL,12,F"I have shown them that nothing is
OL,13,Fimpossible," he said after completing
OL,14,Fthe run in one hour, 59 minutes, and
OL,15,F30 seconds.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1777367169
OL,3,CHow a 97g 'super shoe' helped make
OL,4,Cmarathon history in London
OL,6,F"I was ready today... I'm so happy
OL,7,Fbecause I had a lot of courage to
OL,8,Fpush, even when the pace was fast," he
OL,9,Fsaid. "It's something not to be
OL,10,Fforgotten, something to be remembered,
OL,11,Fand it will remain in my mind forever."
OL,13,FFinishing in second, just 11 seconds
OL,14,Fbehind was Ethiopian Yomif Kejelcha,
OL,15,Faged 28.
OL,17,FIn addition to passion and sheer
OL,18,Fdedication to their sport, Sawe and
OL,19,FKejelcha had something else in common:
OL,20,Ftheir choice of footwear on the day.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1777367169
OL,3,CHow a 97g 'super shoe' helped make
OL,4,Cmarathon history in London
OL,6,FWeighing at just 97 grams, Sawe
OL,7,Fpredicted before defending his London
OL,8,Ftitle that the adidas Pro Evo 3s could
OL,9,Fbe a record-breaking pair.
OL,11,FThe shoes were also worn by Tigst
OL,12,FAssefa, who defended her London
OL,13,FMarathon crown in a women's-only world
OL,14,Frecord of two hours, 15 minutes, and
OL,15,F41 seconds.
OL,17,FSo, what is it that makes the design
OL,18,Fof this new "super shoe" so special?
OL,19,FITV News explains here.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
