OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1777367169
OL,3,CHow a 97g 'super shoe' helped make
OL,4,Cmarathon history in London
OL,6,FWhat makes the adidas Adizero Adios
OL,7,FPro Evo 3 so effective?
OL,9,FWeighing at just 97 grams per shoe on
OL,10,Faverage, the Adizero Adios Pro Evo 3
OL,11,Ffollows what adidas describes as
OL,12,F"three years of cutting-edge research".
OL,14,FTo put the shoe's weight into
OL,15,Fperspective, one of these shoes weighs
OL,16,Fabout the same as an average bar of
OL,17,Fsoap, and a little under a Cadbury's
OL,18,FDairy Milk bar.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1777367169
OL,3,CHow a 97g 'super shoe' helped make
OL,4,Cmarathon history in London
OL,6,FAdidas says the Pro Evo 3 is "30%
OL,7,Flighter, delivers 11% greater forefoot
OL,8,Fenergy return, and improves running
OL,9,Feconomy by 1.6% compared to its
OL,10,Fpredecessor".
OL,12,FThe German sportswear brand says this
OL,13,Fgives the shoe record-breaking
OL,14,Fpotential "before it's even laced up".
OL,16,FLightstrike Pro Evo foam fitted inside
OL,17,Fthe shoe weighs 50% less than previous
OL,18,Fiterations, adidas says, adding that
OL,19,F"with a 39mm stack, it maximises
OL,20,Fcushioning, propulsion and energy
OL,21,Freturn across every stride".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1777367169
OL,3,CHow a 97g 'super shoe' helped make
OL,4,Cmarathon history in London
OL,6,FENERGYRIM, a thin carbon fibre cutout
OL,7,Fthat wraps around the perimeter of the
OL,8,Fshow, is also a key component, adidas
OL,9,Fsays, supporting the maximum volume of
OL,10,Ffoam underfoot "while providing
OL,11,Fprecisely tuned stiffness for
OL,12,Fstability".
OL,14,F"This unique interplay of foam and
OL,15,Fcarbon redefines energy return,
OL,16,Fpropulsion and efficiency in a
OL,17,Fsupershoe," the brand says.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1777367169
OL,3,CHow a 97g 'super shoe' helped make
OL,4,Cmarathon history in London
OL,6,F"Even the smallest components ` from
OL,7,Flaces to stitching ` have been
OL,8,Fobsessively refined to deliver
OL,9,Fmarginal gains that make the
OL,10,Fdifference on race day.
OL,12,F"A more efficient outsole design `
OL,13,Ffeaturing strategically placed
OL,14,FContinental rubber in the forefoot to
OL,15,Fprovide reliable traction at high
OL,16,Fspeeds, without compromising weight."
OL,18,FConcerns over sustainability
OL,20,FRetailing at #450 online, the Adizero
OL,21,FAdios Pro Evo 3 does not come cheap.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1777367169
OL,3,CHow a 97g 'super shoe' helped make
OL,4,Cmarathon history in London
OL,6,FWith such a high price tag, one might
OL,7,Fexpect to get plenty of mileage out of
OL,8,Fa shoe, but when it comes to so-called
OL,9,F"super shoes" designed for elite
OL,10,Fathletes, marginal gains appear to
OL,11,Ftrump sustainability.
OL,13,FIn a post related to the Pro Evo 1 in
OL,14,F2023, the eco-focused Green Runners
OL,15,Fclub penned an open letter to adidas
OL,16,FCEO Bjorn Gulden, expressing concerns
OL,17,Fover the brand's marketing of the shoe
OL,18,Fas being single-use.
OL,26,@xD@Go|
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1777367169
OL,3,CHow a 97g 'super shoe' helped make
OL,4,Cmarathon history in London
OL,6,F"For many years, people have
OL,7,Fcampaigned against single-use
OL,8,Fplastics. And slowly, too slowly,
OL,9,Fgovernments are paying heed," the
OL,10,Fgroup wrote.
OL,12,F"But who would have thought that a
OL,13,Fmajor sports brand would have the
OL,14,Faudacity to market a single-use
OL,15,Frunning shoe? We didn't. But perhaps
OL,16,Fwe should have seen it coming.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1777367169
OL,3,CHow a 97g 'super shoe' helped make
OL,4,Cmarathon history in London
OL,6,F"Over the last few years the race for
OL,7,Fthe fastest shoe has seen the lifespan
OL,8,Fof racing shoes fall. And now you give
OL,9,Fus the Adizero Adios Pro Evo 1, a shoe
OL,10,Fdesigned to last one marathon race.
OL,12,F"By promoting these shoes you are in
OL,13,Fdanger of creating a new normal. An
OL,14,Facceptance that people shouldn't
OL,15,Fexpect to get many miles out of their
OL,16,Frunning shoes."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
