PN,31211
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1777367169
OL,3,CHow a 97g 'super shoe' helped make
OL,4,Cmarathon history in London
OL,6,FIn a statement to outdoor activity
OL,7,Fwebsite Outdoors Magic, a spokesperson
OL,8,Ffor Adidas said: "The adidas adizero
OL,9,Fadios Pro Evo 1 is designed with one
OL,10,Fpurpose in mind, to deliver our best
OL,11,Fperforming materials and technologies
OL,12,Fon race day in our lightest ever long-
OL,13,Fdistance shoe.
OL,15,F"We've tested the shoe with a range of
OL,16,Fathletes across different distances,
OL,17,Fand whilst its (sic) not designed with
OL,18,Fthe same longevity as others in our
OL,19,Fadizero range we, and our athlete
OL,20,Fpartners, are confident in the
OL,21,Fperformance."
OL,26,@pD@ROUwD@AOUyD@PpmyD@Tpn}D@MO]
